In terms of dials, still no store for third-party models, but the possibility of sharing its dials via the sharing menu of the Apple Watch app (from the iPhone, therefore), for example with AirDrop. The files can be viewed with the Files application.⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
watchOS 7 will also offer an Infographics Pro dial, which will complement the two Infographics and Modular Infographics already available.  The novelty of this dial is the presence of a tachometer, which measures the average speed from the time required to travel a given distance.⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
The Photos dial currently offers to display selected photos, a photo folder, or photos from recent memories. The future system goes even further by allowing the display of snapshots shared between several users. A shared album in a way, like in the Photos app but directly on the wrist.⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
The Health app, in which you will determine your sleep goal, will also contain suggestions for improving the quality and duration of sleep. The watchOS 7 control center will include a button to start sleep mode (as well as a control for noise detection).⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
